public javax.jms.ConnectionFactory activeMqArtemisConnectionFactory(ActiveMqArtemisConfigurationProperties config)
        Generates a JMSConnectionFactory bean in the application context.

        The bean is a ActiveMQJMSConnectionFactory configured with properties from ActiveMqArtemisConfigurationProperties.

        Parameters:
        config - config settings for ActiveMQ Artemis
        Returns:
        the ActiveMQJMSConnectionFactory defined by the config.
